p.ff023000000000000011: Get Phone Controller URL (modify if you duplicate this project)

p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Builds the URL to access the Phone Controller app
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92:
This builds the url to reach the matching Phone Controller application.

In case you duplicate this project, you must also modify this function to change the tag of the application to be launched.

The `sc.app=*******` URL parameter indicates which app is running. In case you duplicate this project, the Phone Controller will be duplicated as well and will have a new tag in your new project.

You can retrieve the tag of the app by selecting `Show tag` within the contextual menu of the app, and then put that value in the current function in place of `017e2a46ea70b89cdc45`.
